target="category-7"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="subtopic-7-0" value="&lt;b&gt;轮转与补位&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;3 条 · 关键词：双打轮转、轮转、补位、换位" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#AAB8B4;strokeWidth=1.5;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=10;arcSize=5;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="2370" y="1495" width="300" height="82" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="edge-120" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;strokeColor=#7A8A86;strokeWidth=2;" edge="1" parent="1" source="category-7" target="subtopic-7-0"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="video-7-0-0" value="双打实战轮转 无论训练时有多么默契，实战中都会有配合失误，那实战看的就是两个人的容错够不够&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color='#52625E'&gt;medium · score 15&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F9FBFA;strokeColor=#CBD6D2;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=8;arcSize=5;" vertex="1" parent="1" link="https://www.douyin.com/video/7614167503938610417"><mxGeometry x="2700" y="1491" width="290" height="68" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="edge-121" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;strokeColor=#7A8A86;strokeWidth=2;" edge="1" parent="1" source="subtopic-7-0" target="video-7-0-0"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="video-7-0-1" value="双打抓回头 紫电青霜不要去掉低胶，如果一定要去掉低胶，或者已经去掉底胶，就要考虑结合自己的能力，也要换掉拍…&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color='#52625E'&gt;reviewed_transcript · score 9&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#F9FBFA;strokeColor=#CBD6D2;strokeWidth=1;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=8;arcSize=5;" vertex="1" parent="1" link="https://www.douyin.com/video/7656927370758796145"><mxGeometry x="2700" y="1569" width="290" height="68" as="geometry" /></mxCell><mxCell id="edge-122" style="edgeStyle=orthogonalEdgeStyle;rounded=1;orthogonalLoop=1;jettySize=auto;html=1;strokeColor=#7A8A86;strokeWidth=2;" edge="1" parent="1" sourc